      <description>&lt;div class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;precision-health-monitoring-real-time-connectivity-wearable-comfort&#34;  id=&#34;precision-health-monitoring-real-time-connectivity-wearable-comfort&#34;&gt;Precision health monitoring. Real-time connectivity. Wearable comfort.&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;a class=&#34;&#34; href=&#34;#precision-health-monitoring-real-time-connectivity-wearable-comfort&#34; aria-label=&#34;: Precision health monitoring. Real-time connectivity. Wearable comfort.&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;svg aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34; xmlns=&#34;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#34; width=&#34;24&#34; height=&#34;24&#34; viewBox=&#34;0 0 24 24&#34; stroke-width=&#34;2&#34; stroke=&#34;currentColor&#34; fill=&#34;none&#34; stroke-linecap=&#34;round&#34; stroke-linejoin=&#34;round&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;path stroke=&#34;none&#34; d=&#34;M0 0h24v24H0z&#34; fill=&#34;none&#34; /&gt;&#xA;  &lt;path d=&#34;M10 14a3.5 3.5 0 0 0 5 0l4 -4a3.5 3.5 0 0 0 -5 -5l-.5 .5&#34; /&gt;&#xA;  &lt;path d=&#34;M14 10a3.5 3.5 0 0 0 -5 0l-4 4a3.5 3.5 0 0 0 5 5l.5 -.5&#34; /&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/svg&gt;&#xA;&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Whether your patients are managing a chronic condition, recovering from an injury, or simply want peace of mind, &lt;strong&gt;SH+‚Ñ¢ wearable band&lt;/strong&gt; is designed to bring clinical-grade insight to your patients wrist -without interrupting their lives.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;key-features&#34;  id=&#34;key-features&#34;&gt;Key features&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;a class=&#34;&#34; href=&#34;#key-features&#34; aria-label=&#34;: Key features&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;svg aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34; xmlns=&#34;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#34; width=&#34;24&#34; height=&#34;24&#34; viewBox=&#34;0 0 24 24&#34; stroke-width=&#34;2&#34; stroke=&#34;currentColor&#34; fill=&#34;none&#34; stroke-linecap=&#34;round&#34; stroke-linejoin=&#34;round&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;path stroke=&#34;none&#34; d=&#34;M0 0h24v24H0z&#34; fill=&#34;none&#34; /&gt;&#xA;  &lt;path d=&#34;M10 14a3.5 3.5 0 0 0 5 0l4 -4a3.5 3.5 0 0 0 -5 -5l-.5 .5&#34; /&gt;&#xA;  &lt;path d=&#34;M14 10a3.5 3.5 0 0 0 -5 0l-4 4a3.5 3.5 0 0 0 5 5l.5 -.5&#34; /&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/svg&gt;&#xA;&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;h3 id=&#34;-imu-inertia-measuring-unit&#34;  id=&#34;-imu-inertia-measuring-unit&#34;&gt;üß≠ IMU (Inertia Measuring Unit)&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;a class=&#34;&#34; href=&#34;#-imu-inertia-measuring-unit&#34; aria-label=&#34;: üß≠ IMU (Inertia Measuring Unit)&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;svg aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34; xmlns=&#34;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#34; width=&#34;24&#34; height=&#34;24&#34; viewBox=&#34;0 0 24 24&#34; stroke-width=&#34;2&#34; stroke=&#34;currentColor&#34; fill=&#34;none&#34; stroke-linecap=&#34;round&#34; stroke-linejoin=&#34;round&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;path stroke=&#34;none&#34; d=&#34;M0 0h24v24H0z&#34; fill=&#34;none&#34; /&gt;&#xA;  &lt;path d=&#34;M10 14a3.5 3.5 0 0 0 5 0l4 -4a3.5 3.5 0 0 0 -5 -5l-.5 .5&#34; /&gt;&#xA;  &lt;path d=&#34;M14 10a3.5 3.5 0 0 0 -5 0l-4 4a3.5 3.5 0 0 0 5 5l.5 -.5&#34; /&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/svg&gt;&#xA;&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Track body movement, posture, and fall events with a high-precision IMU. From subtle shifts to sudden impacts, &lt;strong&gt;SH+‚Ñ¢ wearable band&lt;/strong&gt; captures motion data in real time‚Äîuseful for physical therapy monitoring, elderly care, and fall detection.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;h3 id=&#34;-pulse-sensor&#34;  id=&#34;-pulse-sensor&#34;&gt;üíó Pulse Sensor&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;a class=&#34;&#34; href=&#34;#-pulse-sensor&#34; aria-label=&#34;: üíó Pulse Sensor&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;svg aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34; xmlns=&#34;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#34; width=&#34;24&#34; height=&#34;24&#34; viewBox=&#34;0 0 24 24&#34; stroke-width=&#34;2&#34; stroke=&#34;currentColor&#34; fill=&#34;none&#34; stroke-linecap=&#34;round&#34; stroke-linejoin=&#34;round&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;path stroke=&#34;none&#34; d=&#34;M0 0h24v24H0z&#34; fill=&#34;none&#34; /&gt;&#xA;  &lt;path d=&#34;M10 14a3.5 3.5 0 0 0 5 0l4 -4a3.5 3.5 0 0 0 -5 -5l-.5 .5&#34; /&gt;&#xA;  &lt;path d=&#34;M14 10a3.5 3.5 0 0 0 -5 0l-4 4a3.5 3.5 0 0 0 5 5l.5 -.5&#34; /&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/svg&gt;&#xA;&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Continuously monitor heart rate with a built-in optical pulse sensor. Whether it&amp;rsquo;s resting, active, or irregular rhythms, our system detects it and flags anomalies for review by health professionals or caregivers.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;h3 id=&#34;-buzzer-alert-system&#34;  id=&#34;-buzzer-alert-system&#34;&gt;üì¢ Buzzer-alert system&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;a class=&#34;&#34; href=&#34;#-buzzer-alert-system&#34; aria-label=&#34;: üì¢ Buzzer-alert system&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;svg aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34; xmlns=&#34;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#34; width=&#34;24&#34; height=&#34;24&#34; viewBox=&#34;0 0 24 24&#34; stroke-width=&#34;2&#34; stroke=&#34;currentColor&#34; fill=&#34;none&#34; stroke-linecap=&#34;round&#34; stroke-linejoin=&#34;round&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;path stroke=&#34;none&#34; d=&#34;M0 0h24v24H0z&#34; fill=&#34;none&#34; /&gt;&#xA;  &lt;path d=&#34;M10 14a3.5 3.5 0 0 0 5 0l4 -4a3.5 3.5 0 0 0 -5 -5l-.5 .5&#34; /&gt;&#xA;  &lt;path d=&#34;M14 10a3.5 3.5 0 0 0 -5 0l-4 4a3.5 3.5 0 0 0 5 5l.5 -.5&#34; /&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/svg&gt;&#xA;&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Local alerts ensure you (or the wearer) never miss a critical event. When thresholds are crossed‚Äîlike abnormal heart rate or lack of movement‚Äîa discreet buzzer provides instant feedback, even before the cloud gets the message.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;h3 id=&#34;-wi-fi-enabled-gateway-to-cloud-connectivity&#34;  id=&#34;-wi-fi-enabled-gateway-to-cloud-connectivity&#34;&gt;üì∂ Wi-Fi Enabled: Gateway-to-Cloud Connectivity&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;a class=&#34;&#34; href=&#34;#-wi-fi-enabled-gateway-to-cloud-connectivity&#34; aria-label=&#34;: üì∂ Wi-Fi Enabled: Gateway-to-Cloud Connectivity&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;svg aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34; xmlns=&#34;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#34; width=&#34;24&#34; height=&#34;24&#34; viewBox=&#34;0 0 24 24&#34; stroke-width=&#34;2&#34; stroke=&#34;currentColor&#34; fill=&#34;none&#34; stroke-linecap=&#34;round&#34; stroke-linejoin=&#34;round&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;path stroke=&#34;none&#34; d=&#34;M0 0h24v24H0z&#34; fill=&#34;none&#34; /&gt;&#xA;  &lt;path d=&#34;M10 14a3.5 3.5 0 0 0 5 0l4 -4a3.5 3.5 0 0 0 -5 -5l-.5 .5&#34; /&gt;&#xA;  &lt;path d=&#34;M14 10a3.5 3.5 0 0 0 -5 0l-4 4a3.5 3.5 0 0 0 5 5l.5 -.5&#34; /&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/svg&gt;&#xA;&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SH+‚Ñ¢ wearable band&lt;/strong&gt; doesn&amp;rsquo;t just collect data‚Äîit sends it where it matters. Through Wi-Fi connectivity to a local gateway, vital signs and motion data are securely transmitted to the cloud, enabling real-time dashboards, alerts, and remote monitoring by healthcare providers or family.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;-secure-and-scalable&#34;  id=&#34;-secure-and-scalable&#34;&gt;üõ°Ô∏è Secure and Scalable&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;a class=&#34;&#34; href=&#34;#-secure-and-scalable&#34; aria-label=&#34;: üõ°Ô∏è Secure and Scalable&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;svg aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34; xmlns=&#34;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#34; width=&#34;24&#34; height=&#34;24&#34; viewBox=&#34;0 0 24 24&#34; stroke-width=&#34;2&#34; stroke=&#34;currentColor&#34; fill=&#34;none&#34; stroke-linecap=&#34;round&#34; stroke-linejoin=&#34;round&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;path stroke=&#34;none&#34; d=&#34;M0 0h24v24H0z&#34; fill=&#34;none&#34; /&gt;&#xA;  &lt;path d=&#34;M10 14a3.5 3.5 0 0 0 5 0l4 -4a3.5 3.5 0 0 0 -5 -5l-.5 .5&#34; /&gt;&#xA;  &lt;path d=&#34;M14 10a3.5 3.5 0 0 0 -5 0l-4 4a3.5 3.5 0 0 0 5 5l.5 -.5&#34; /&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/svg&gt;&#xA;&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;End-to-end encryption&lt;/strong&gt; from device to cloud.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Modular APIs&lt;/strong&gt; for integration into existing health platforms.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Cloud dashboards&lt;/strong&gt; with customizable alert thresholds.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;OTA firmware updates&lt;/strong&gt; to future-proof your device.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;-who-is-it-for&#34;  id=&#34;-who-is-it-for&#34;&gt;üìà Who is it for?&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;a class=&#34;&#34; href=&#34;#-who-is-it-for&#34; aria-label=&#34;: üìà Who is it for?&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;svg aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34; xmlns=&#34;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#34; width=&#34;24&#34; height=&#34;24&#34; viewBox=&#34;0 0 24 24&#34; stroke-width=&#34;2&#34; stroke=&#34;currentColor&#34; fill=&#34;none&#34; stroke-linecap=&#34;round&#34; stroke-linejoin=&#34;round&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;path stroke=&#34;none&#34; d=&#34;M0 0h24v24H0z&#34; fill=&#34;none&#34; /&gt;&#xA;  &lt;path d=&#34;M10 14a3.5 3.5 0 0 0 5 0l4 -4a3.5 3.5 0 0 0 -5 -5l-.5 .5&#34; /&gt;&#xA;  &lt;path d=&#34;M14 10a3.5 3.5 0 0 0 -5 0l-4 4a3.5 3.5 0 0 0 5 5l.5 -.5&#34; /&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/svg&gt;&#xA;&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Elderly and at-risk individuals&lt;/strong&gt; needing passive, continuous monitoring&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Clinics, retirement homes and hospitals&lt;/strong&gt; deploying wearable tech for outpatient care&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Researchers&lt;/strong&gt; gathering granular motion and vitals data&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Caregivers&lt;/strong&gt; who need real-time insight into their loved one‚Äôs health&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;-technical-specifications-short-version&#34;  id=&#34;-technical-specifications-short-version&#34;&gt;üîß Technical specifications (short version)&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;a class=&#34;&#34; href=&#34;#-technical-specifications-short-version&#34; aria-label=&#34;: üîß Technical specifications (short version)&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;svg aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34; xmlns=&#34;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#34; width=&#34;24&#34; height=&#34;24&#34; viewBox=&#34;0 0 24 24&#34; stroke-width=&#34;2&#34; stroke=&#34;currentColor&#34; fill=&#34;none&#34; stroke-linecap=&#34;round&#34; stroke-linejoin=&#34;round&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;path stroke=&#34;none&#34; d=&#34;M0 0h24v24H0z&#34; fill=&#34;none&#34; /&gt;&#xA;  &lt;path d=&#34;M10 14a3.5 3.5 0 0 0 5 0l4 -4a3.5 3.5 0 0 0 -5 -5l-.5 .5&#34; /&gt;&#xA;  &lt;path d=&#34;M14 10a3.5 3.5 0 0 0 -5 0l-4 4a3.5 3.5 0 0 0 5 5l.5 -.5&#34; /&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/svg&gt;&#xA;&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;table&gt;&#xA;  &lt;thead&gt;&#xA;      &lt;tr&gt;&#xA;          &lt;th&gt;Feature&lt;/th&gt;&#xA;          &lt;th&gt;Specs&lt;/th&gt;&#xA;      &lt;/tr&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/thead&gt;&#xA;  &lt;tbody&gt;&#xA;      &lt;tr&gt;&#xA;          &lt;td&gt;IMU&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;          &lt;td&gt;High resolution 3-axis accelerometer&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;      &lt;/tr&gt;&#xA;      &lt;tr&gt;&#xA;          &lt;td&gt;Pulse Sensor&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;          &lt;td&gt;Light-reflection signaling (PPG)&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;      &lt;/tr&gt;&#xA;      &lt;tr&gt;&#xA;          &lt;td&gt;Connectivity&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;          &lt;td&gt;2.4GHz Wi-Fi (802.11 b/g/n)&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;      &lt;/tr&gt;&#xA;      &lt;tr&gt;&#xA;          &lt;td&gt;Alerts&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;          &lt;td&gt;On-device buzzer (configurable)&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;      &lt;/tr&gt;&#xA;      &lt;tr&gt;&#xA;          &lt;td&gt;Power&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;          &lt;td&gt;Rechargeable Li-ion battery&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;      &lt;/tr&gt;&#xA;      &lt;tr&gt;&#xA;          &lt;td&gt;Cloud-compatibility&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;          &lt;td&gt;MQTT / REST API, HTTPS&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;      &lt;/tr&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/tbody&gt;&#xA;&lt;/table&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;-ready-for-deployment&#34;  id=&#34;-ready-for-deployment&#34;&gt;‚úÖ Ready for Deployment&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;a class=&#34;&#34; href=&#34;#-ready-for-deployment&#34; aria-label=&#34;: ‚úÖ Ready for Deployment&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;svg aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34; xmlns=&#34;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#34; width=&#34;24&#34; height=&#34;24&#34; viewBox=&#34;0 0 24 24&#34; stroke-width=&#34;2&#34; stroke=&#34;currentColor&#34; fill=&#34;none&#34; stroke-linecap=&#34;round&#34; stroke-linejoin=&#34;round&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;path stroke=&#34;none&#34; d=&#34;M0 0h24v24H0z&#34; fill=&#34;none&#34; /&gt;&#xA;  &lt;path d=&#34;M10 14a3.5 3.5 0 0 0 5 0l4 -4a3.5 3.5 0 0 0 -5 -5l-.5 .5&#34; /&gt;&#xA;  &lt;path d=&#34;M14 10a3.5 3.5 0 0 0 -5 0l-4 4a3.5 3.5 0 0 0 5 5l.5 -.5&#34; /&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/svg&gt;&#xA;&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Whether you&amp;rsquo;re a healthcare provider, system integrator, or researcher, &lt;strong&gt;SH+‚Ñ¢ wearable band&lt;/strong&gt; offers a flexible and secure solution for remote health monitoring. Deployment support and custom firmware options available upon request.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;</description>
